title: IS THIS THE RISE OF JAYCE?
body:
Jayce JG? you might think it is a troll pick but your enemies won't see this coming
BOOM massive shockwave plus melee swap q and a perfect e to made escaping harder for your enemies is all you need to do to carry your games

replies.body: you just have to believe it will work
follow your link, it doesn't work.
Did this heaps last season, worked well, im not playing jayce at the moment due to him having a bug with casting eq near river will result in no empowered q. Be careful of invade junglers.

>Sorry we fragged that page awhile ago and it's too traumatized to show its face around here anymore.

Lol

Jayce jungle would be pretty trash.
i like how this is trying to be a serious post. nice try

yeah...I don't think so...its like udyr, you need to flash to get them unless theyre not paying attention. And plus, jayce q has a massive animation time in which he can be cc'd or dashed away from. Only thing he's good at in jg imo is clearing w/ his mana back per attack n aoe
